description:
Learn Google Maps JavaScript API course provides a jump start for beginners and the complete guide for GIS professionals of using Google Maps JS API.

Course covers 

  • Map and Controls.
  • Shapes and Geometries.
  • Overlays (Markers, Raster ...etc.)
  • Data Layers (JSON, KML ... Etc.)
  • Events and Behaviors.
  • API Services.
  • Practice Projects.

In this course we'll practice together, every mapping concept with SampleCode as well as practice projects. 

By the end of the course, you will be able to build complete web mapping applications using Google Maps.
title: Learn Google Maps JavaScript API
